## Current Behavior

I just migrated to nx 14.8.3.
Previous was 14.4.0

I'm serving my application using this command:
```
nx myapp:serve:development
```

This is the project.json inside myapp :

```
"targets": {
    "build": {
      "executor": "@nrwl/next:build",
      "outputs": ["{options.outputPath}"],
      "defaultConfiguration": "production",
      "dependsOn": [],
      "options": {
        "root": "apps/myapp",
        "outputPath": "dist/apps/myapp",
        "assets": [
          {
            "glob": "**/*",
            "input": "libs/auth/public/html",
            "output": "html"
          },
          {
            "glob": "**/*",
            "input": "libs/shared-ui/public/fonts",
            "output": "fonts"
          },
          {
            "glob": "**/*",
            "input": "libs/i18n/public/locales",
            "output": "locales"
          },
          {
            "glob": "**/*",
            "input": "libs/shared-ui/public/images",
            "output": "images"
          },
          {
            "glob": "**/*",
            "input": "libs/shared/public/images",
            "output": "images"
          }
        ]
      },
      "configurations": {
        "development": {},
        "production": {}
      }
    },
"serve": {
      "executor": "@nrwl/next:server",
      "defaultConfiguration": "development",
      "options": {
        "buildTarget": "myapp:build",
        "port": 3000
      },
      "configurations": {
        "development": {
          "buildTarget": "myapp:build:development",
          "dev": true
        },
        "production": {
          "buildTarget": "myapp:build:production",
          "dev": false
        }
      }
    }
}
```

## Issue

The dev application is not serving anymore the asset files from other libraries. (logo, fonts, etc..)

## Expected Behavior
It was correctly serving the asset files from other libraries before (last version working was 14.4.0)
I tested all nx imports and the @nrwl/nx is creating the issue starting, all other libs can be updated to 14.8.3.

